comment.narrative: 3 training programs (Carpentry, Air-Conditioning, and Metal Fabrication) designed but not implemented

baseline.value: Baseline for regular courses is 7603; baseline value for short-term courses is (3230+1964) = 5194

target.value: 2% increase in regular courses; 5% in short-term courses

actual.value: 12% increase from baseline in 2012 for regular courses§ 11% decrease from baseline in 2012 for short-term courses

baseline.value: Baseline value for regular courses is 1938; baseline value for short-term courses is 1866 + 165sq) = 2031

target.value: 2% increase in regular courses; 5% in short-term courses

actual.value: 36% increase from baseline in 2012 for regular courses§ 42% decrease from baseline in 2012 for short-term courses
